        "title": "最后一刻临时追加！黄仁勋加入特朗普访华代表团",
        "uri": "https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3772146"
      },
      "author": {
        "avatar": "https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/714916ad-9609-4245-94b4-dfe9518a63c3",
        "display_name": "万小婷",
